<view class='h1'>
填写的淘宝账号和买家性别，请与截图上显示的会员名称、性别保持一致，信息无法修改
</view>
<view class='form big'>
   <view class='form-ctrl'>
      <label>淘宝账号</label>
      <input class='txt ' placeholder='请输入淘宝账号或手机号'></input>
   </view>
   <view class='warnning'>
   温馨提示：淘宝账号指的是淘宝会员名，不是手机、QQ或者邮箱哦
   </view>
<view class='bd'></view>
   <view class='form-ctrl'>
      <label>性别</label>
      <view class='txt'>
         <radio-group>
          <radio>男</radio><radio class='ml20'>女</radio>
         </radio-group>
      </view>
   </view>
   <view class='form-ctrl'>
      <label>会员等级</label>
      <picker  class="txt" bindchange="bindPickerChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{array}}">
    <view>
     {{array[index]}}
    </view>
  </picker>
   </view>
</view>
<view class='form mt20'>
  <view class='h1'>
    上传【我的淘宝截图】
  </view>
   <view class='bd mt20' ></view>
  <view class='upload'>
    <view class='item1'>
      <block wx:for="{{imgs}}" wx:for-index="idx" wx:for-item="item" wx:key='item'>
      <image class='img' mode='aspectFill' id='{{idx}}' src='{{item}}' bindtap='tapImage'></image>
      </block>
      <text>个人资料截图</text>
      <text>会员中心截图</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<text class='h1 '>请仔细填写以上信息，并注意填写的支付宝账户、昵称和绑定的身份证持有人保持一致，一面对您的体现造成影响
</text>
   <button class='btn' bindtap='submit'>提交审核</button>
   